Hardware License (KiCad Design Files)
The hardware design files in this repository are licensed under the CERN Open Hardware Licence Version 2 - Weakly Reciprocal (CERN-OHL-W-2.0).
You are free to:
✔ Use, modify, and distribute the hardware design.
✔ Sell the hardware, either as-is or with modifications.
✔ Use it for personal or commercial projects.
Requirements:
    Attribution: You must credit the original author when distributing or selling the hardware.
    Modifications: If you modify the hardware, you must document the changes and provide proper attribution to the original work.
    No additional restrictions: You may not impose legal terms that restrict others from exercising the rights granted under this license.
Full license text: [CERN-OHL-W-2.0](https://ohwr.org/project/cernohl/wikis/Documents/CERN-OHL-version-2)

Firmware License (Binary-Only, Apache 2.0)
The firmware in this repository is licensed under Apache License 2.0 but is only available in compiled binary form. The source code is not provided.
You are free to:
✔ Use the firmware for personal or commercial purposes.
✔ Distribute the firmware binary as long as you include this license.
You are not allowed to:
❌ Modify or reverse-engineer the firmware.
❌ Distribute the firmware's source code (since it is not provided).
Full license text: [Apache 2.0](https://www.apache.org/licenses/LICENSE-2.0)

For any commercial inquiries regarding firmware modifications or licensing, please contact the author.
